product.title: Japanese Sakura Cherry Blossom Kimono
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Sakura kimonos are beautiful, practical and timeless wardrobe garment 

    They're a visual feast of traditional Japanese art. Kimonos for men and women feature vivid designs with seasonal sakura cherry blossoms, goldfish carp and other iconic images. Japanese goldfish carp, a symbol of prosperity and happiness.

    With a classic oversized look, this light, thin kimono will feel silky soft on your skin. 12 unique styles to choose from that will have everyone wanting one of their own. Wear it at home, wear it the next time you're out with friends, or even take it with you to Japan!

      

    Stand out the next time you're out

    A stylish, cute kimono top that goes with any tee and outfit ready to make a statement. These kimonos are made from premium quality polyester giving them a very soft touch and smooth feeling. 

    Available in 4 different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below. Please be sure that this kimono fits you before purchasing! Please accept our apologies if this kimono does not fit you.

    Size (inches) M L XL XXL
    Bust 49 51 52 54
    Length 27 27 28 28
    Sleeve 11 11 11 12
             
    Size (cm) M L XL XXL
    Bust 126 130 134 138
    Length 69 70 71 72
    Sleeve 27 28 29 30



    Features

    ✨ Made with premium polyester
    ✨ Features Japanese iconic images
    ✨ 12 styles available
    ✨ Lightweight smooth feel


    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
